From 08af009335602efac15a5895f4d68fda127f98fe Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RivonClaw CI <ci@rivonclaw.com>
Date: Sat, 27 Jun 2026 17:59:11 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] vendor(openclaw): add cpu debugging diagnostics

Why:
- RivonClaw needs switchable high-CPU diagnostics for stale model calls, reload deferral, and task inspection without changing default runtime behavior.

Removal:
- Drop after upstream exposes equivalent CPU/debug diagnostics for stuck model calls, restart blockers, and task registry inspection.

Tests:
- apps/desktop/test/vendor-patch-cpu-debugging.test.ts
- src/tasks/task-registry.cpu-debugging.e2e.test.ts
- corepack pnpm exec node scripts/tsdown-build.mjs
